# CDNav Fields

1. selectableVariant (string) 
   - "default" or "xDemo" 
   - Controls the variant rendered

2. title (string) 
   - The primary title displayed if logo is missing

3. subtitle (string) 
   - Additional line shown near the title or under it

4. logo (image)
   - Optional logo image

5. links (array of objects)
   - label (string)
   - url (string)

6. backgroundColor (string)
   - hex or named color to style the nav background

7. sortOrder (number)
   - used for ordering multiple components

8. globalComponentSource (reference)
   - re-usable source for the nav